snippet.title: M*A*S*H for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Was sold both with and without M*A*S*H  T-shirt.

The game also included an entry form for the '$25,000 M*A*S*H Game Design Contest', but it is unknown if anyone actually ever collected the prize.
